<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p class="meta">Arrow Puzzle · MindByte Studio · Last updated: March 2026</p>

<p>MindByte Studio built the <strong>Arrow Puzzle</strong> app as a free app.
This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and
disclosure of personal information when you use our app.</p>

<h2>Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
<p>Arrow Puzzle does <strong>not</strong> collect, transmit, or share any
personal information. We do not collect your name, email address, location,
device identifiers, or any other personally identifiable information.</p>

<h2>Local Data Storage</h2>
<p>The app saves your game progress locally on your device. This data:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Never leaves your device</li>
  <li>Is never sent to any server</li>
  <li>Can be cleared by clearing app data</li>
</ul>

<h2>No Ads, No Tracking</h2>
<p>Arrow Puzzle contains no advertisements and no analytics or tracking services.</p>

<h2>No Internet Required</h2>
<p>The app works fully offline. No network requests are made during gameplay.</p>

<h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>We do not knowingly collect personal information from anyone, including
children under 13. The app is suitable for all ages.</p>

<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>If we update our data practices, we will update this page and the date above.</p>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>Questions? Email: <a href="mailto:mindbytestudio@gmail.com">mindbytestudio@gmail.com</a></p>
